title: Default values are not shown in Show Report Parameters' dialog
OB: After previewing the report, click the Show Report Parameters button.
EB: Expected behavior: The default values should be displayed in the value box, allowing the user to modify the parameter they want to change.
SR:
1. Open the report.
2. Preview the report.
3. Click the Show Report Parameters button.
4. Observe that the default values are not displayed in the Enter Parameters dialog.
5. Attempt to modify a parameter and notice that all the values are empty.
